Titolo: Dave Mirra BMX Challenge

Anno: 2006

Descrizione: Dave Mirra BMX Challenge is a racing video game by Crave Entertainment for the PlayStation Portable and later for the Nintendo Wii. The game is an entry of the Dave Mirra franchise. It would be the only entry released by Crave Entertainment after previous publisher of the series, Acclaim Entertainment, filed for bankruptcy in 2004, and would eventually be the final entry of the series released before Mirra's death in 2016.